        "text": "",
        "text_original": "じゃあ私のことも……守ってくれる？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_3_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_lobby_4_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "こっちの書類は終わったよ。結構キツかったー！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_4_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_lobby_4_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "まぁ、先生の役に立ってるならいいんだけどさ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_4_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_lobby_5_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ん？レオパード柄？好きだよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_lobby_5_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "銃以外にも色々レオパード柄で揃えたりしてるくらいにはね♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_lobby_5_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "他に持ってるレオパード柄の私物？ふふっ……教えてあーげない♪",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_lobby_5_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_login_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "やっほ、先生♪待ってたよ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_login_2_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "おかえり！会いたかった。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_2_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_login_2_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "（ちょっと待って……私今なんて？）",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_login_2_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_1_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ようこそ、先生。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_1_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_1_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ここが、私だけの秘密基地――",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_1_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_2_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "一人の時間が欲しい時に、来る場所。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_2_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_2_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ふふっ、でも秘密基地っていうには、ちょっと広いかも。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_2_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_3_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "……なんか、先生に共有したかったんだよね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_3_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_3_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "私がいつも見ている景色とか……感じてる空気、とか。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_3_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "理由を聞かれてもなんとなく、しか言えないんだけど……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "そうだね……秘密の場所を教えるのって、特別の証だからさ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_4_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生は、私の特別な人ってこと。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_4_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "……ふふっ。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ここは静かでしょ？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_memoriallobby_5_3",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "まあでも……私の心は、ちょっと騒がしいんだけどね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_memoriallobby_5_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_relationship_up_1",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "最近先生とよく会うかも？なんでだろね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_relationship_up_2",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "なんかいっぱいくれるじゃん。嬉しいけど……もらってばっかはなぁ。先生は欲しいもの、ある？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_relationship_up_3",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "んー……クセになりそ。あんまり甘やかさないでよ？困っちゃう。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_3.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_relationship_up_4",
        "category": "growup",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ほんとさ……先生が甘やかすからダメになっちゃいそ。……もう。私ばっかドキドキさせられてる気がするんだけど？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_relationship_up_4.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_birthday_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "えっ……私の誕生日、覚えてたの？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_birthday_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生って本当に罪づくりな人だよね。……期待、させちゃってどうする気？",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_birthday_player",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "先生、お誕生日おめでと～！世界の誰よりも幸せな日でありますよーに！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_birthday_player.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_halloween_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ガオーッ！お菓子くれなきゃ食べちゃうぞ！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_halloween_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_halloween_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ほら、食べられないように頑張って。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_halloween_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_newyear",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "あけましておめでとう、先生！今年もいっぱい思い出作ろうね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_newyear.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_xmas_1",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "クリスマスっていい日だよね。雰囲気がワクワクするっていうか、ドキドキするっていうか……。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_xmas_1.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_season_xmas_2",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "特別な日って感じ……一緒にいるだけで、ね。",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_season_xmas_2.ogg"
      },
      {
        "description": "erika_Title",
        "category": "lobby",
        "text": "",
        "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ！",
        "file": "https://static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%97%97%E8%A7%81%20%E7%BB%98%E9%87%8C%E9%A6%99/original/jp/erika_Title.ogg"
      }
    ],
